<note>The note on <locus target="#22v">f. 22v</locus> states that the text was translated from Arabic into
Gǝʿǝz by <persName role="translator" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS8387SalamaI">ʾAbbā Salāmā</persName>.</note>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
